These are Puzzles for 6x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 6x4-Level-2-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: milk, iced-tea, mirinda, sprite
There 4 different types of food: grapefruit, raspberry, kale, asparagus
The people have 4 different hobbies: traveling, hiking, board-games, filmmaking
The people have 4 different jobs:  nurse, scientist, pilot, police-officer
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: soul, house, trance, punk
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: snowboarding, cricket, soccer, rowing
 1. the police-officer is on the far right##1
 2. the person drinking mirinda is the fan of soul##1
 3. the fan of house is on the left of the fan of trance##1
 4. the person eating kale is on the left of the person eating raspberry##1
 5. the person drinking sprite is the person eating asparagus##1
 6. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
 7. the pilot is between the person who's sport is snowboarding and the fan of punk##2
 8. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the right of the person who's sport is rowing##1
 9. the fan of soul is on the right of the nurse##1
10. the person who's sport is snowboarding is between the pilot and the person eating asparagus##2
11. the person eating grapefruit is on the right of the person who's sport is cricket##1
12. the police-officer is the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
13. the fan of trance is between the fan of house and the person who's hobby is board-games##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |     3     |      4      |
| Beverage      | sprite        | iced-tea       | mirinda  | milk |
| Food          | asparagus     | kale         | raspberry     | grapefruit    |
| Hobby         | hiking  | traveling      | board-games   | filmmaking     |
| Job           | scientist | nurse | pilot   | police-officer     |
| Music-Genre   | house    | trance         | soul | punk         |
| Sport         | rowing     | snowboarding     | cricket  | soccer       |

