.:: Puzzle 6x4-Level-2-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: water, iced-tea, coffee, milk
The people have 4 different hobbies: traveling, baking, card-games, reading
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: romance, horror, scientific, superhero
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: rock, funk, punk, salsa
There are 4 different nationalities: american, nigerian, italian, french
The people use 4 different means of transport: van, boat, helicopter, skateboard
 1. the nigerian is between the person who's hobby is card-games and the person driving the van##2
 2. the french is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1
 3. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left of the american##1
 4. the nigerian is between the person drinking water and the person driving the helicopter##2
 5. the fan of rock is the person drinking iced-tea##1
 6. the fan of punk is on the far right##1
 7. the person who's hobby is baking is on the right of the fan of funk##1
 8. the person driving the helicopter is between the person watching romance movies and the person who's hobby is reading##2
 9. the person watching horror movies is the person who's hobby is reading##1
10. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the far left##1
11. the fan of rock is the person watching scientific movies##1
12. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1
13. the italian is on the right of the person driving the boat##1
14. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the nigerian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3      |      4      |
| Beverage      | milk    | iced-tea       | coffee   | water |
| Hobby         | traveling     | card-games   | reading    | baking  |
| Movie-Genre   | romance    | scientific | horror   | superhero     |
| Music-Genre   | salsa    | rock       | funk | punk        |
| Nationality   | french | italian   | nigerian     | american    |
| Transport     | boat       | helicopter        | skateboard      | van        |

