.:: Puzzle 6x4-Level-2-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, sprite, soy-milk, coffee
There 4 different types of food: lettuce, banana, strawberry, tomato
There are 4 different nationalities: german, canadian, thai, italian
4 different pets are kept: ferret, cat, goldfish, frog
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: volleyball, cycling, badminton, tennis
The people use 4 different means of transport: roller, bike, train, scooter
 1. the canadian is on the right of the person eating strawberry##1
 2. the owner of the goldfish is on the right of the person who's sport is tennis##1
 3. the person who's sport is cycling is on the right of the owner of the ferret##1
 4. the person eating banana is on the left of the italian##1
 5. the person who's sport is tennis is the person drinking soy-milk##1
 6. the owner of the frog is on the far right##1
 7. the person driving the scooter is between the thai and the person drinking coffee##2
 8. the person drinking sprite is the owner of the cat##1
 9. the person drinking cola is between the person driving the scooter and the owner of the ferret##2
10. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
11. the person drinking coffee is the person driving the train##1
12. the person eating strawberry is the person driving the bike##1
13. the owner of the goldfish is between the person eating lettuce and the canadian##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |       3       |    4     |
| Beverage      | soy-milk      | cola        | sprite | coffee      |
| Food          | lettuce   | strawberry       | banana          | tomato   |
| Nationality   | german     | thai    | canadian      | italian  |
| Pet           | ferret    | goldfish     | cat       | frog      |
| Sport         | tennis | cycling    | badminton        | volleyball |
| Transport     | roller       | bike | scooter           | train   |

