The people have 4 different hobbies: biked-games, singing, dancing, video-games
The people have 4 different jobs:  coach, analyst, dressmaker, pilot
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: epic, zombie, mystery, superhero
There are 4 different nationalities: canadian, turkish, mexican, argentine
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, quad-bike, trike, snowmobile
 1. the person drinking iced-tea is between the person who's hobby is singing and the mexican##2
 2. the person drinking juice is on the left of the analyst##1
 3. the person driving the quad-bike is on the right of the person watching zombie movies##1
 4. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
 5. the argentine is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1
 6. the person watching zombie movies is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
 7. the dressmaker is on the left of the canadian##1
 8. the person driving the trike is the person watching superhero movies##1
 9. the person driving the bike is between the dressmaker and the person who's hobby is biked-games##2
10. the mexican is on the left of the person watching epic movies##1
11. the person who's hobby is biked-games is on the left of the person driving the bike##1
12. the pilot is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
13. the person drinking juice is the person drinking juice##1
14. the person who's hobby is dancing is the canadian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |         2          |     3      |     4     |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate        | iced-tea              | juice      | sprite  |
| Hobby         | biked-games | video-games            | singing | dancing |
