 8. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1
 9. the person drinking soy-milk is on the far left##1
10. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left of the person watching family movies##1
11. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
12. the french is on the left of the person driving the tram##1
13. the person drinking water is on the left of the italian##1

