There 4 different types of food: pepper, grapefruit, garlic, orange
The people have 4 different jobs:  dressmaker, accountant, nurse, scientist
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: d&b, punk, gospel, jazz
There are 4 different nationalities: chinese, thai, russian, italian
4 different pets are kept: cat, ferret, pony, guinea-pig
